API keys required 
- Scraper(place in a .env file in the folder) =
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/
CALENDARIFIC_API_KEY
GEMINI_API_KEY
APININJAS_API_KEY

frontend (.env file contents)=
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8080

Description Generation (.env content)=
GEMINI_API_KEY


Emailer (.env content)=
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/
GMAIL_ADDRESS=ediprojectcalendarapplication@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD= Generate app password using google.com
setup a cronjob that runs on the first of every month
